{"tid":1724134,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我認為必須編制《抗爭者守則》以防情況失控","createTime":"2019-11-15T11:27:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T12:57:52.000Z","uid":60291,"like":105,"dislike":52,"uniUserReply":56,"replies":[{"pid":"adfc6e0dd19c8d0bac48922b1e89bf33940afc6b","tid":1724134,"uid":60291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T11:27:13.000Z","msg":"我唔係左膠  亦無潔癖 但不得不承認呢個世界好多人 包括國際 都有好多底線 而我地要贏 都必須獲得佢地嘅支持同力量<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地 唔係暴徒 但亦明白 作為人 會有情緒 同時必須要有底線 小弟係度大膽提議 編制《抗爭者守則》 以約束自己 防止做出影響整個運動勝負嘅事<br />\n<br />\n如果呢個PO獲得3000以上正評 小弟會嘗試編制一份簡潔易明嘅守則 以大家參考"},{"pid":"66b950ed3e89d744fa5b5b75fecff9e9dd18288c","tid":1724134,"uid":60291,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T11:28:54.000Z","msg":"亦可以有效防止被抹黑"},{"pid":"f0c7da07d811f51018831f85bcaa38b724c71112","tid":1724134,"uid":60291,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T11:30:40.000Z","msg":"習曱甴"},{"pid":"34b54282af7cb36c8293ddb7c235c857cb84079b","tid":1724134,"uid":60291,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T11:32:00.000Z","msg":"例子 不向地鋪或有機會引起嚴重傷亡嘅場所施放火魔法"},{"pid":"5ad4a8e368e215b3cdc2755e76662ae2046190e5","tid":1724134,"uid":42042,"like":21,"dislike":10,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T11:32:14.000Z","msg":"自己有分數啦<br />\n唔洗你指指點點<br />\n<br />\n一有守則就會內閧<br />\n加速失敗"},{"pid":"d011f1ddb7913b4d838cac8f49b30f61e24cfc87","tid":1724134,"uid":263756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T11:32:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5499565e0ffb15553dcfd9d950bdf43813ca55a3","tid":1724134,"uid":165682,"like":13,"dislike":4,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T11:32:47.000Z","msg":"啱<br />\n條道德線開始比風向撚吹到好蒙糊<br />\n係咪贏就可以無視所有野<br />\n係咪講其他意見就係分化<br />\n係咪唔可以虛心聽下意思"},{"pid":"08828def3941eecdb665878ce7da74b8adf92a85","tid":1724134,"uid":60291,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"5ad4a8e368e215b3cdc2755e76662ae2046190e5","tid":1724134,"uid":42042,"like":21,"dislike":10,"score":1